      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 **Budget-Friendly Project Car \u2014 Priced for What It Is!** Looking for an affordable entry point or a hands-on project? This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has significant mechanical and cosmetic issues that will require real attention and investment to address. It's not a daily driver as-is, but for the right buyer with the skills and patience, there's potential here! Priced honestly to reflect its current state \u2014 no surprises, just a straightforward deal.",
