    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable & Ready to Go \u2014 A Solid Choice for Smart Buyers! This well-maintained used car is in good condition and ready to be your next dependable ride. The exterior shows only minor signs of normal wear, and the paint still holds up nicely overall. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable \u2014 nothing flashy, but everything you need for a pleasant daily drive. Mechanically, it runs well and has been cared for responsibly. If you want a trustworthy vehicle without paying mint-condition prices, this one is well worth your attention!",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
