      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in poor shape and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project car, parts vehicle, or someone with the mechanical skills and resources to bring it back to roadworthy condition. The exterior shows significant wear, including rust, dents, and faded or damaged paint. The interior is worn and shows its age, with torn upholstery, broken trim pieces, and general neglect throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues and should not be expected to run reliably without repairs. We are not aware of a recent service history, and there may be additional issues a thorough inspection would reveal. This is a straightforward, no-surprises listing \u2014 what you see is what you get. Priced accordingly for the right buyer who knows what they're taking on.",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $19,500, a price that honestly reflects its fair overall condition. The exterior shows visible wear beyond normal use \u2014 expect multiple scratches, some paint fading, and possibly a small dent or two. The interior is functional but shows clear signs of age and use, including worn upholstery and some scuffs on trim pieces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but prospective buyers should be aware that it may benefit from some maintenance or repairs in the near term \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. This is a practical, budget-conscious option for a buyer who doesn't mind putting a little work into a vehicle or simply needs reliable transportation without paying a premium for cosmetic perfection.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride or a project car with real potential? This vehicle is priced to move and offers a genuine opportunity for the budget-conscious buyer or a handy DIYer! We'll be upfront \u2014 this car is in poor condition, showing significant wear both inside and out, and will likely need some mechanical attention to get it running at its best. But at this price point, it's a solid starting point for someone ready to roll up their sleeves or simply needs basic transportation on a tight budget. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This is an exceptional opportunity to own a vehicle in truly mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you'll find on the used car market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with a deep, lustrous paint finish free of scratches, chips, or swirl marks. Every panel is straight and true, and the chrome and trim pieces shine as if the car just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally impressive: the upholstery shows no wear, fading, or staining, and all surfaces, controls, and electronics function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean, dry, and performs with full power and responsiveness. All fluids are fresh, and there are no warning lights or mechanical concerns whatsoever. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, and the brakes are in top condition. This vehicle has clearly been meticulously cared for throughout its life, and a new owner can expect to drive it with complete confidence from day one. If you're looking for a used car that truly feels new, this is it.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
